---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Lick Metronome"
  description="Privacy policy for the Lick metronome app."
>
  <div class="page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: May 11, 2026</p>

    <p>Lick is a metronome app built by Érik Escobedo. This app is provided at no cost and is intended for use as is.</p>

    <h2>Information Collection</h2>
    <p>Lick does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. The app does not require an account, does not access the internet, and does not use analytics or advertising SDKs.</p>

    <h2>Device Permissions</h2>
    <p>Lick does not request any special device permissions.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Lick does not use any third-party services.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions, contact <a href="mailto:erik@escobedo.dev">erik@escobedo.dev</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: var(--prose-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .updated {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-3);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--blue);
  }
</style>
